title: LF Dynamic Duo Partner
body: Hey guys silver 3 Adc main looking for a support main to duo with, want to climb the ranks and hopefully get into gold soon, dont be toxic or salty.

replies.body:
I'm also looking for an ADC to support or just anyone to duo with in general. I'm a former S2 that has had a terrible time this season 6 due to dynamic soloQ. Currently B3 but can for sure play on a higher level. I also got Curse, Raidcall, Discord and ... yes Skype. I'm on every evening till late. 
IGN: Kiryuuin Satsuki
I could duo with you, currently climbing out of B4 and main support
Sure thing. I accepted your invite and will see you on SR soon.
I'll be on at around 7.00 later tonight. I will support you. Prepare to have mind blown.

Hey i have added u in game. i am only ranked b3 ATM but was in silver before a harsh demote back to bronze. I main Nami, Poppy, Tahm, Alistar and Braum as supps. I am keen as anything to get out of this bronze hell i'm stuck in and back to rising the ranked ladder once more.
